chore(build): fix ui-kit

Moved ui-kit .less files, svg and fonts to assets.
It is now the same path in both development and production

fix(pci): don't retry openstack client if expired

fix to make it stop retrying openstack client if the session is expired

chore(pci): refactor ssh key

Refactor SSH Keys page. In addition to the obvious beneficial changes of
using Cloud services, the body of the POST does not contain the params
required in the URL

Remove body from POST call when not needed. API now see it as a
security leak.
